<root>
   <descrip>Hildebrand, Who was frightened by a Passing Motor, and was brought to Reason. </descrip>
   <lg num="1">
      <l num="1">“Oh, Murder! What was that, Papa!”</l>
      <l num="2"> “My child, It was a Motor-Car,</l>
      <l num="3">A Most Ingenious Toy!</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-40.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a car speeding down the road</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="2">
      <l num="1">Designed to Captivate and Charm </l>
      <l num="2"> Much rather than to rouse Alarm</l>
      <l num="3"> In any English Boy.</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-41.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a man with his hand on a childs head</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="3">
      <l num="1">“What would your Great Grandfather who </l>
      <l num="2">Was Aide-de-Camp to General Brue,</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-42.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a general on a horse</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="4">
      <l num="1">And lost a leg at Waterloo, </l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-43.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a man hopping on one leg</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="5">
      <l num="1">And Quatre-Bras and</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-44.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a man hopping on one leg again</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="6">
      <l num="1">Ligny too!</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-45.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a man hopping on one leg and falling</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="7">
      <l num="1">And died at Trafalgar!—</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-46.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a man being shot on a bridge</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
   <lg num="8">
      <l num="1"> What would he have remarked to hear</l>
      <l num="2">His Young Descendant shriek with fear,</l>
      <l num="3">Because he happened to be near</l>
      <l num="4">A Harmless Motor-Car!</l>
      <l num="5">But do not fret about it! Come!</l>
      <l num="6">We’ll off to Town And purchase some!”</l>
      <picture url="../docs/illus/CTC-47.jpg">
         <interp resp="sqm">a man and a young boy with a line of cars behind them</interp>
      </picture>
   </lg>
</root>
